<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Inventory Alert: Item Below Threshold</h1>
    
    <p>This is an automated notification to inform you that the following item has fallen below its threshold value:</p>

    <div style="margin: 20px; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
      <h2><%= @item.name %></h2>
      <p><strong>Current Quantity:</strong> <%= @inventory_item.quantity %></p>
      <p><strong>Threshold Value:</strong> <%= @inventory_item.threshold %></p>
    </div>

    <p>Please take necessary action to restock this item.</p>

    <p>
      Best regards,<br>
      Inventory Management System
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
